{"tid":170581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾俊華造勢晚會，3 5 0 0 人出席，迫爆龍和道","createTime":"2017-03-24T19:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T17:30:17.000Z","uid":58099,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c7c06131b6a5e980f6566411bdcd616df2b20f9","tid":170581,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T19:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/o8s64maz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fo8s64maz&h=8ef484ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特首候選人曾俊華星期五巡遊造勢，晚上在愛丁堡廣場舉辦集會。<br />\n<br />\n他在集會尾聲的發言提到，集會地點旁邊是龍和道及干諾道中，兩年半前佔中就在附近發生，希望今晚的集會為該處賦予新意義。與會者聞言即鼓掌並高呼「曾俊華當選」。集會期間，巿民亮起手機電筒以示支持。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，集會最高峰時有3500人。曾俊華競選辦則表示，競選辦沒有統計到場人數，但對大批巿民出席熱烈支持表示感謝。"},{"pid":"28199d0a0467567714300ebe72d6da3e45204d3e","tid":170581,"uid":10774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T19:36:50.000Z","msg":"以為你自殺死左"},{"pid":"f3c534789388e48fc847d5c7205f5e11fda1c395","tid":170581,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T19:55:40.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"499ea1c05b1c7206008d28606626cdf39f2f576b","tid":170581,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T20:14:10.000Z","msg":"有無唱返首海闊天空"},{"pid":"bf5cf0f576973046ab4271bf2451ffb7de0d29e1","tid":170581,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T21:11:46.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"bfd2b5382d74b706caa3c40c4985251ca3955149","tid":170581,"uid":36696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T21:15:52.000Z","msg":"龍和道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://holland.pk/4jtxqlk3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4jtxqlk3&h=413fb380&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c225110f012d1a78117d1bf0bb2a907b7eb5f95d","tid":170581,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T21:18:24.000Z","msg":"<